-- Noir --

"Not very long..." She frowns, "I knew there was some holes in my 
memory, but this proves that it is worse than I had originally 
thought..." The last part trails off as she begins to speak quietly 
to herself.

She comes out of her thoughts when Devilcat brings up a view of what 
looks like another base or something. Noir isn't sure where, or how 
they are getting these images. "Devilcat, what are these images?"


--- In nbwrpg@y..., "cardhead649" <cardhead649@y...> wrote:
> Devilcat/Gatara/Riekan::
> 
> "Not very long, as Riekan informs me."  The leader of the Rogues 
has 
> other things on his mind, however.  "Now, how is our little friend 
> doing?"
> 
> By this he means Phoenix.  Gatara turns to her readouts again and 
> punches up a different view - the Pred base through Phoenix's eyes.
> 
> "Not too shabby, it would seem," Riekan comments, deadpan.
